WEBVTT

01:42.720 --> 01:47.200
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL ZHU YU
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

01:51.240 --> 01:53.480
These pheasants were hard won today.

01:53.560 --> 01:55.960
We will roast them later
and give the men a proper taste of meat.

01:57.000 --> 01:58.320
Let me handle that.

01:58.400 --> 01:59.880
Last time you didn't pluck them clean.

01:59.960 --> 02:01.320
The men complained it tasted terrible.

02:01.400 --> 02:03.560
-You tend the fire. I will do it.
-All right.

02:03.640 --> 02:06.160
You cannot just throw pheasants
in hot water.

02:06.240 --> 02:07.760
Rinse them in cold water first
to tighten the skin.

02:07.840 --> 02:09.360
Then scald them in boiling water
for half an incense stick.

02:09.440 --> 02:11.080
That way, the feathers come off clean.

02:12.640 --> 02:14.560
You are quite the cook for a young lady.

02:16.080 --> 02:17.120
How about this?

02:17.200 --> 02:20.120
Join our fire unit. Cannot promise riches,

02:20.200 --> 02:23.000
but if we have meat to eat,
you will have your share too.

02:23.680 --> 02:25.800
Thank you, sir, but I cannot.

02:25.880 --> 02:28.400
My husband is injured.
He needs looking after.

02:28.480 --> 02:30.320
Once he is well, I will come help out.

02:30.400 --> 02:31.960
All right, all right.

02:32.040 --> 02:32.880
Good.

02:36.680 --> 02:37.760
Mrs. Fan.

02:38.360 --> 02:39.680
Mr. Sun… No.

02:40.400 --> 02:41.640
Strategist.

02:41.720 --> 02:42.760
Do you need something?

02:42.840 --> 02:44.120
Yes. I have good news.

02:44.200 --> 02:45.880
All right. Come. Sit.

02:46.960 --> 02:47.880
Thank you.

02:49.320 --> 02:51.520
The soldiers have set up
a new tent over there.

02:51.600 --> 02:52.760
Yan Zheng has been moved.

02:53.360 --> 02:55.200
-Really?
-It is quieter there.

02:55.280 --> 02:57.160
You can brew his medicine in peace.

02:57.240 --> 02:58.440
That is wonderful.

03:00.400 --> 03:01.960
But there are so many wounded.

03:02.040 --> 03:03.560
Why move only him?

03:06.280 --> 03:07.200
Well…

03:08.360 --> 03:11.400
You played a key part
in the flood stratagem.

03:11.480 --> 03:14.160
You even risked your life
to find your husband.

03:14.880 --> 03:16.480
When Marquis Wu'an heard,

03:16.560 --> 03:18.240
he ordered this as a reward for him.

03:18.840 --> 03:20.440
Only words of praise?

03:20.520 --> 03:21.680
Nothing more tangible?

03:23.200 --> 03:24.040
There is.

03:28.000 --> 03:28.840
For you.

03:33.040 --> 03:35.000
That is hardly enough to share.

03:37.200 --> 03:38.520
That is not all.

03:44.840 --> 03:47.160
Everyone in the Pig-Slaughter Squad
receives a reward.

03:47.960 --> 03:50.320
For… everyone?

03:52.000 --> 03:53.080
So much.

03:55.040 --> 03:56.520
That is wonderful.

03:56.600 --> 03:58.600
A noble lord like the Marquis,

03:58.680 --> 04:01.080
yet he keeps common folk like us in mind.

04:02.600 --> 04:03.720
When Yan Zheng recovers,

04:03.800 --> 04:05.680
we will go thank him in person.

04:05.760 --> 04:07.000
That will not be necessary.

04:07.680 --> 04:10.520
I'll pass along your gratitude
to His Lordship.

04:10.600 --> 04:11.560
I will take my leave.

04:16.560 --> 04:19.200
I must get the money back from Xie Zheng.

04:20.279 --> 04:21.880
-One!
-Kill!

04:22.560 --> 04:24.520
-Two!
-Kill!

04:24.600 --> 04:26.040
-One!
-Kill!

04:26.120 --> 04:27.760
-Two!
-Kill!

04:27.840 --> 04:29.080
This is a new powder I made.

04:29.680 --> 04:31.680
It works wonders for healing wounds
and helps to regenerate tissues.

04:31.760 --> 04:32.640
WOUND SALVE

04:32.720 --> 04:34.560
I heard you tasted hundreds of herbs

04:34.640 --> 04:36.120
before finding one that was safe.

04:36.200 --> 04:39.120
On behalf of the soldiers, I thank you.

04:39.720 --> 04:40.960
It's my duty as Imperial Physician.

04:49.280 --> 04:50.600
There is something I must ask you.

04:51.360 --> 04:53.000
Why did you lie to Fan Changyu?

04:53.920 --> 04:55.120
She may be commonly born,

04:55.200 --> 04:57.720
but I cannot bear to see
such a good woman be wronged.

04:59.960 --> 05:01.720
Other than concealing
my title as Marquis Wu'an,

05:01.800 --> 05:03.760
I have not deceived her in the slightest.

05:06.400 --> 05:08.080
You would do well
to tend to your own affairs.

05:08.160 --> 05:09.600
Mine are none of your concern.

05:10.320 --> 05:12.520
Marquis Wu'an is worlds apart…

05:15.360 --> 05:16.440
Marquis Wu'an?

05:19.200 --> 05:21.240
-You were speaking of the Marquis?
-Changyu.

05:21.320 --> 05:23.080
What is this about rank
being worlds apart?

05:24.000 --> 05:25.160
What happened?

05:26.520 --> 05:27.560
Tell me.

05:30.720 --> 05:33.600
Is there some vast difference in status
between Yan Zheng and the Marquis?

05:35.200 --> 05:36.800
Well…

05:36.880 --> 05:40.120
He was teaching Marquis Wu'an
how to hide private savings.

05:40.200 --> 05:41.440
Private savings?

05:43.000 --> 05:44.960
Even the Marquis hides money?

05:45.560 --> 05:46.840
Just like Mr. Zhao.

05:46.920 --> 05:49.480
So you had better
keep a tight rein on Yan Zheng.

05:49.560 --> 05:51.720
If the Marchioness finds out,

05:51.800 --> 05:53.800
he will be in deep trouble.

05:53.880 --> 05:55.440
Honestly.

05:55.520 --> 05:57.600
You can barely lie straight,

05:57.680 --> 05:59.840
and yet you give the Marquis
advice like that.

06:03.640 --> 06:05.800
All right. I will leave you two
to your sweet talk.

06:05.880 --> 06:06.800
I'll go brew medicine.

06:10.080 --> 06:11.920
The fire unit caught a few pheasants.

06:12.000 --> 06:14.080
I bought one for you.
You need proper nourishment.

06:16.880 --> 06:17.720
Here.

06:27.360 --> 06:28.640
It smells good.

06:29.200 --> 06:30.880
Just lacking a touch of salt.

06:30.960 --> 06:31.960
Might taste a bit gamey.

06:33.120 --> 06:34.280
I can manage.

06:41.480 --> 06:42.400
Look.

06:45.240 --> 06:46.120
What is this?

06:46.960 --> 06:50.520
The Marquis heard
about us intercepting the scouts at Baxia.

06:50.600 --> 06:51.840
He rewarded me and the squad.

06:52.600 --> 06:54.400
I have money now. I can provide for you.

06:55.880 --> 06:56.720
Good.

06:58.960 --> 07:00.200
Tell me something.

07:00.280 --> 07:02.760
When you climbed the mountain,
did it never cross your mind

07:03.280 --> 07:04.920
that you might not make it back down?

07:05.520 --> 07:07.120
The Marquis is formidable.

07:07.200 --> 07:09.480
He would never let us die trapped here.

07:10.200 --> 07:12.840
And if the rebels really break through,

07:12.920 --> 07:14.320
I can still get you out.

07:16.040 --> 07:17.320
If that day comes,

07:17.400 --> 07:19.760
just think of saving yourself.

07:19.840 --> 07:21.080
Why bring me along?

07:21.720 --> 07:22.840
Why not?

07:22.920 --> 07:24.840
I said I would provide for you.

07:24.920 --> 07:26.040
I meant it.

07:30.880 --> 07:33.880
When you left Lin'an, I struck you.

07:34.720 --> 07:36.360
I said hurtful things.

07:37.800 --> 07:40.240
Every time I think of it, I feel awful.

07:40.320 --> 07:41.240
Ashamed.

07:45.640 --> 07:46.480
So,

07:47.240 --> 07:48.800
you only came here

07:49.440 --> 07:50.360
because of guilt?

07:51.200 --> 07:52.480
No. That's not it.

07:53.160 --> 07:54.000
I…

07:54.520 --> 07:55.920
Not just guilt.

07:57.560 --> 07:58.640
You probably didn't know.

07:59.360 --> 08:02.080
On the road here, I nearly lost my life.

08:04.880 --> 08:06.520
When Lin'an was massacred,

08:06.600 --> 08:08.600
that brute came seeking revenge.

08:08.680 --> 08:11.360
I almost fell off a cliff.

08:12.360 --> 08:15.240
If not for a kind old lady,
I would have died.

08:17.400 --> 08:18.560
I am not afraid of death.

08:19.840 --> 08:21.680
I was afraid Changning
would lose her sister.

08:24.720 --> 08:26.240
I was afraid I would never see you again.

08:34.320 --> 08:35.280
I missed you.

08:37.679 --> 08:39.080
I was terrified you were dead.

08:40.960 --> 08:42.080
Do not die.

08:42.600 --> 08:44.640
Come home with me. All right?

08:49.800 --> 08:50.640
All right.

09:24.800 --> 09:25.800
I slept so long.

09:26.520 --> 09:28.200
Wake me up next time.

09:30.240 --> 09:31.120
Sleep if you are tired.

09:48.320 --> 09:49.200
What is it?

09:50.640 --> 09:51.480
Nothing.

09:55.280 --> 09:56.440
I just remembered

09:56.520 --> 09:59.120
when I dragged you home from the snow.

10:00.240 --> 10:02.000
You were far worse than this.

10:02.640 --> 10:03.560
Your whole face

10:04.600 --> 10:07.320
was caked in blood.
I couldn't even tell what you looked like.

10:13.520 --> 10:14.400
Here.

10:16.200 --> 10:18.360
Now I have nursed you back again.

10:22.960 --> 10:24.000
Does it still hurt?

10:26.240 --> 10:27.120
With you here,

10:28.760 --> 10:29.600
not so much.

10:59.520 --> 11:00.360
Your hand.

11:31.080 --> 11:32.120
Changyu.

11:56.640 --> 11:57.840
You kissed me.

12:03.560 --> 12:04.560
I…

12:05.880 --> 12:06.720
I just…

12:29.240 --> 12:30.520
We are even now.

12:45.320 --> 12:46.920
I will come see you in the morning.

12:48.640 --> 12:49.640
Rest well.

13:16.360 --> 13:17.320
Look at that shine.

13:19.160 --> 13:20.520
Feels heavy too, Cang.

13:20.600 --> 13:22.600
That Marquis Wu'an sure is generous.

13:22.680 --> 13:23.520
Here.

13:24.760 --> 13:26.360
-Yuanbao.
-Yuanbao.

13:26.440 --> 13:27.480
Did you find Changyu?

13:28.760 --> 13:29.600
I did.

13:30.560 --> 13:31.400
Good.

13:31.960 --> 13:32.920
Good.

13:33.760 --> 13:35.200
She found her live-in husband too.

13:35.920 --> 13:36.760
She did?

13:37.800 --> 13:39.680
Look at all this silver.

13:46.960 --> 13:48.160
Changyu is happy.

13:49.080 --> 13:50.120
That makes me happy too.

13:51.720 --> 13:52.880
Happy. Very happy.

13:52.960 --> 13:55.080
I say our luck is finally turning.

13:55.680 --> 13:56.520
How so?

13:56.600 --> 13:58.480
Look. Changyu found her man.

13:58.560 --> 13:59.800
We got reward money.

13:59.880 --> 14:01.520
More of Lin'an's folks are still alive.

14:01.600 --> 14:04.080
-There is a phrase for that. What is it?
-What phrase?

14:04.160 --> 14:06.480
-The one where everyone ends up well.
-Everyone ends up well?

14:06.560 --> 14:07.760
Best of both worlds.

14:08.520 --> 14:09.680
That's it.

14:09.760 --> 14:11.280
-Yuanbao truly has learning.
-So refined.

14:11.360 --> 14:12.200
I couldn't even think of it.

14:12.280 --> 14:13.560
-As expected of Yuanbao.
-No wonder

14:13.640 --> 14:15.040
-you get things done.
-Quiet down!

14:15.120 --> 14:16.280
People are trying to sleep.

14:18.400 --> 14:20.240
You… You lot again?

14:20.320 --> 14:21.400
You again?

14:21.480 --> 14:22.320
Come back here.

14:28.960 --> 14:29.800
Get over here.

14:40.000 --> 14:41.640
Come on. Drink.

14:42.960 --> 14:44.360
Come on. Bottoms up.

14:52.560 --> 14:53.400
Drink.

15:03.920 --> 15:04.760
Changyu.

15:23.840 --> 15:26.680
Changyu, I am cold.

15:27.400 --> 15:28.240
Here.

15:29.800 --> 15:30.800
Tuck yourself in.

16:07.480 --> 16:08.880
His wounds are so severe.

16:10.360 --> 16:12.400
How can he return to the battlefield?

16:26.000 --> 16:28.680
I am freezing.

16:33.840 --> 16:35.960
Might as well go sleep with Zheng.

16:42.400 --> 16:45.400
XIE

16:50.760 --> 16:51.800
Strategist!

16:53.520 --> 16:54.760
Her High…

16:54.840 --> 16:56.000
The Imperial Physician…

16:56.080 --> 16:58.240
-What happened?
-Come with me.

17:08.200 --> 17:09.160
Your Highness!

17:23.200 --> 17:26.760
Jianjia, this prescription works well
for internal injuries.

17:27.440 --> 17:29.800
Distribute it to the other physicians
at once.

17:29.880 --> 17:31.760
Tell them to start brewing.

17:40.280 --> 17:41.600
Why are you here?

17:43.360 --> 17:45.160
You wore yourself down

17:46.160 --> 17:47.680
just to prepare these medicines?

17:48.840 --> 17:50.320
I tested them myself.

17:51.120 --> 17:52.720
The herbs are harmless.

17:52.800 --> 17:53.920
They can be found anywhere.

17:54.960 --> 17:55.800
You…

17:56.760 --> 17:58.000
You tasted them yourself?

17:58.080 --> 18:00.280
Her Highness has sampled
countless herbs already.

18:00.880 --> 18:02.320
She can barely taste anymore.

18:03.160 --> 18:04.280
There's no salt in camp anyway.

18:04.880 --> 18:06.200
Perhaps that is a blessing.

18:06.280 --> 18:08.000
Saves me from tasting anything foul.

18:10.960 --> 18:12.880
The medicine is ready. Go, Jianjia.

18:17.880 --> 18:19.480
You are the Grand Princess.

18:20.000 --> 18:21.120
Of the highest rank.

18:21.200 --> 18:23.160
How can you act
with such disregard for yourself?

18:23.240 --> 18:24.960
Right now, I am an imperial physician.

18:25.040 --> 18:27.600
I came to this army to save lives.

18:27.680 --> 18:29.600
Fine. Even if you are a physician,

18:29.680 --> 18:31.440
these herbs are unverified.

18:31.520 --> 18:32.640
What if they were poisonous?

18:32.720 --> 18:34.680
-They could have killed you.
-And if they had?

18:34.760 --> 18:36.080
I told you.

18:36.880 --> 18:38.720
Do not treat me as a Grand Princess.

18:39.600 --> 18:41.520
You are not at the academy now.

18:42.160 --> 18:44.200
In what position do you question me?

18:47.000 --> 18:49.720
Did you not once teach at the academy,

18:50.400 --> 18:54.200
"A ruler must bear the duty
to shelter his people?"

18:55.200 --> 18:58.720
A ruler must bear the duty
to shelter his people.

18:59.400 --> 19:02.240
The sovereign of a nation
must shoulder the heavy burden

19:02.320 --> 19:04.800
of protecting all under Heaven.

19:07.920 --> 19:09.680
That is the way between
the emperor and ministers.

19:10.480 --> 19:12.640
You are the Grand Princess,
born to privilege,

19:13.200 --> 19:14.400
as a delicate lady,

19:15.720 --> 19:17.360
yet you push yourself so harshly.

19:19.920 --> 19:22.440
It is precisely because
I bear the title of Grand Princess,

19:23.200 --> 19:24.800
because I enjoy the blessings
of the people,

19:25.680 --> 19:28.560
that I am all the more bound
to protect them.

19:29.600 --> 19:30.800
Is that not so?

19:43.880 --> 19:45.160
In that case,

19:45.240 --> 19:47.640
if their pain can be eased,

19:48.400 --> 19:49.440
then this battle

19:50.680 --> 19:52.160
still holds a chance of victory.

20:03.480 --> 20:05.280
Your Highness,
it is time for your medicine.

20:06.760 --> 20:07.880
What is this?

20:07.960 --> 20:10.200
She has been tasting herbs every day.
Some may carry poison.

20:10.280 --> 20:12.880
This is the antidote decoction
she prepared in advance.

20:13.680 --> 20:14.720
Let me.

20:20.400 --> 20:22.280
So you are not entirely foolish.

20:23.440 --> 20:25.360
At least you thought
to prepare an antidote.

20:30.360 --> 20:31.200
Here.

20:32.280 --> 20:33.520
Who are you calling foolish?

20:37.320 --> 20:38.160
Me.

20:39.400 --> 20:40.440
Here.

20:41.000 --> 20:42.160
All right, me.

20:43.280 --> 20:44.120
Slowly.

20:54.560 --> 20:56.240
That wretched girl who delivered the grain

20:56.320 --> 20:58.280
is the one His Highness
ordered us to capture alive.

21:00.120 --> 21:02.320
And she is no ordinary woman.

21:03.040 --> 21:06.480
She killed three of our scouts
and even stabbed His Highness once.

21:07.600 --> 21:10.320
Cold-hearted. Bold beyond reason.

21:10.400 --> 21:12.160
Had I ambushed the supply unit myself,

21:12.840 --> 21:14.720
I wouldn't have let
such a chance at merit slip away.

21:14.800 --> 21:17.160
Shi Hu, remember this.

21:17.240 --> 21:19.640
As long as His Highness
remains in their hands,

21:19.720 --> 21:21.760
we do nothing rash.

21:21.840 --> 21:23.520
Then how long do we endure?

21:23.600 --> 21:26.040
Prince Changxin waits for us
to join him at Lucheng.

21:26.120 --> 21:27.880
We will not endure forever.

21:28.680 --> 21:30.280
But to deal with Marquis Wu'an,

21:31.000 --> 21:32.440
we must use strategy.

21:32.960 --> 21:35.000
A frontal assault will cost too much.

21:40.400 --> 21:42.200
Better to break them from all sides.

21:42.960 --> 21:44.600
Let despair seep into their camp.

21:44.680 --> 21:46.160
When their morale falters, we strike.

21:47.400 --> 21:50.400
-But His Highness's safety--
-We wait until Marquis lowers his guard.

21:51.160 --> 21:53.640
Only then can we seize the heir back.

21:54.720 --> 21:57.000
XIE

22:03.280 --> 22:04.680
Hurry up. Move it.

22:04.760 --> 22:06.520
Why are we assembling this early?

22:08.200 --> 22:09.240
Do you smell that?

22:10.280 --> 22:11.560
Roasted meat.

22:14.080 --> 22:16.440
Smells incredible.

22:19.320 --> 22:20.600
Give me a piece.

22:20.680 --> 22:22.720
It smells so good.

22:22.800 --> 22:24.600
I have not tasted meat in ages.

22:24.680 --> 22:26.560
Roast meat? Where? Find it.

22:26.640 --> 22:28.600
-Where?
-Over there.

22:32.120 --> 22:33.240
WOUND SALVE

22:37.480 --> 22:38.320
Xie…

22:40.800 --> 22:41.680
Yan Zheng.

22:41.760 --> 22:43.360
Come in. No one else is here.

22:45.760 --> 22:46.960
Good news.

22:48.160 --> 22:50.600
You had the men below the mountain
scrape turf and dig up roots.

22:50.680 --> 22:52.200
The rebels took the bait.

22:52.280 --> 22:54.320
They truly believe
we are out of provisions.

22:54.880 --> 22:58.800
Now they are on the east and south sides,
roasting mutton,

22:58.880 --> 23:01.200
trying to shake our morale.

23:01.280 --> 23:03.960
Shi Yue actually thought of that trick.

23:04.040 --> 23:05.400
He has a brain, I'll grant him that.

23:05.480 --> 23:07.160
They underestimate us.

23:07.240 --> 23:09.600
Every son of Yanzhou has spine.

23:10.360 --> 23:11.480
Even if we had nothing left

23:12.160 --> 23:13.720
but bark and roots,

23:13.800 --> 23:16.320
we would never surrender
to such crude theatrics.

23:16.400 --> 23:18.520
A brain, perhaps. Not much of one.

23:18.600 --> 23:19.920
Exactly.

23:22.640 --> 23:23.680
Proceed as planned.

23:24.560 --> 23:25.400
Yes.

23:28.880 --> 23:31.840
-What is that smell?
-Yeah. What is that smell?

23:31.920 --> 23:33.520
Where is that coming from?

23:33.600 --> 23:36.400
The smell of that roast meat is torture.

23:41.880 --> 23:43.000
Hurry.

23:53.240 --> 23:54.120
Sir.

23:54.200 --> 23:56.880
Do you know where
the lightly wounded camp went?

23:57.800 --> 23:59.200
The rebels are roasting sheep below.

23:59.280 --> 24:00.200
The whole camp is on alert.

24:00.280 --> 24:03.440
The lightly wounded…
must have been urgently summoned.

24:06.440 --> 24:07.720
He has gone back out?

24:08.360 --> 24:09.560
His wounds have not even healed.

24:13.120 --> 24:14.200
Sir.

24:14.280 --> 24:16.480
Do you know where they were sent?

24:16.560 --> 24:18.720
-I do not.
-Asking about military secrets

24:18.800 --> 24:19.880
can cost you your head.

24:21.600 --> 24:23.920
I am only worried
about Yan Zheng's injury.

24:25.920 --> 24:27.640
Your live-in husband is capable.

24:27.720 --> 24:29.760
Skilled and sharp. He will be fine.

24:30.840 --> 24:32.520
No matter how capable he is,

24:32.600 --> 24:33.920
he is still a foot soldier.

24:34.600 --> 24:36.640
He must charge at the front.

24:40.480 --> 24:44.720
Even Marquis Wu'an charges first
to protect the rest.

24:51.040 --> 24:53.080
Then I can only hope
the Marquis protects him as well.

24:57.600 --> 24:58.560
Changyu!

25:00.320 --> 25:01.320
-Ning.
-What's wrong?

25:01.920 --> 25:03.120
The cave…

25:06.440 --> 25:07.680
In the cave…

25:07.760 --> 25:09.320
What happened in the cave? Slowly.

25:10.360 --> 25:12.280
That bad man.

25:12.360 --> 25:14.920
I saw him get captured.

25:15.000 --> 25:17.120
They locked him inside the cave.

25:20.440 --> 25:21.640
Please watch her for me.

25:24.160 --> 25:26.120
Ning, who is this bad man?

25:26.200 --> 25:27.080
What did he do?

25:27.160 --> 25:31.320
I saw him in Xigu Alley, killing people.

25:37.480 --> 25:39.800
High-security prisoner inside.
No one enters without leave.

25:40.840 --> 25:43.280
I just want to know one thing.

25:43.800 --> 25:46.440
Is the beast in there Sui Yuanqing?

25:46.520 --> 25:49.000
Is that Mrs. Fan I hear?

25:49.600 --> 25:51.240
So you came after all.

25:54.400 --> 25:56.240
Seems Heaven truly bound
our fates together.

25:57.120 --> 25:59.960
-Come to rekindle old feelings?
-I will butcher you right now!

26:00.040 --> 26:01.080
Orders are iron. Do not invite trouble.

26:01.160 --> 26:02.000
To hell with your iron orders.

26:02.080 --> 26:02.960
My mother is dead.

26:03.040 --> 26:04.280
Why does he get to live?

26:04.360 --> 26:05.240
Hold!

26:07.880 --> 26:10.400
Mrs. Fan, I know why you are here.

26:11.000 --> 26:14.040
But the prisoner inside
holds the balance of this war.

26:14.120 --> 26:15.640
He is a dangerous but necessary piece.

26:16.240 --> 26:17.520
He cannot die yet.

26:18.120 --> 26:19.560
I only want to ask him one thing.

26:21.040 --> 26:22.760
Why did he slaughter Lin'an?

26:24.320 --> 26:25.840
Those innocent townsfolk…

26:26.960 --> 26:28.840
What wrong had they done?

26:30.280 --> 26:31.800
Then step inside.

26:32.320 --> 26:33.920
Come in, and I will tell you.

26:34.000 --> 26:35.240
-I will kill you.
-Fine!

26:37.840 --> 26:38.920
You alone may enter.

26:40.040 --> 26:41.160
Hand me the blade.

27:07.240 --> 27:08.400
-Open the gate.
-Yes.

27:14.960 --> 27:17.400
The blood is still fresh,
yet we meet again.

27:17.480 --> 27:18.520
Mrs. Fan,

27:18.600 --> 27:20.760
I think of you every day.

27:21.440 --> 27:24.240
How about you? Do you ever think of me?

27:26.200 --> 27:27.200
I think of you

27:28.880 --> 27:30.520
dying a miserable death.

27:34.880 --> 27:36.920
Why did you massacre Lin'an?

27:39.760 --> 27:41.000
Why?

27:42.440 --> 27:43.600
Because I felt like it.

27:44.480 --> 27:46.840
Xie Zheng wanted to shield Lin'an.

27:47.360 --> 27:49.360
I would not let him have his way.

27:50.160 --> 27:51.760
If you were from Lin'an,

27:52.920 --> 27:54.400
you were meant to die.

27:58.440 --> 28:00.360
So you did it just to spite him?

28:02.520 --> 28:04.160
You spared no one,

28:05.200 --> 28:07.400
not even women and children.

28:08.880 --> 28:10.840
They were but ants.

28:13.840 --> 28:15.160
So angry.

28:15.240 --> 28:16.720
Shall I continue?

28:16.800 --> 28:18.560
That little sister of yours…

28:18.640 --> 28:19.920
That

28:20.440 --> 28:22.160
sickly little wretch.

28:22.840 --> 28:24.560
I tied her to my horse as I rode.

28:24.640 --> 28:27.080
She could not bear the jolting.
Vomited the whole way.

28:27.160 --> 28:28.680
Nearly drowned her in the river too.

28:28.760 --> 28:30.560
The look on her face

28:31.320 --> 28:32.920
was priceless.

28:36.840 --> 28:39.640
And that constable of yours.
Stubborn to the end.

28:40.240 --> 28:43.080
Still died under my blade.

28:45.000 --> 28:46.720
Then the magistrate's daughter.

28:46.800 --> 28:48.560
She refused to tell me where you were.

28:48.640 --> 28:51.240
I did not hesitate. One thrust.

28:51.320 --> 28:53.040
Blood sprayed three feet high.

29:04.720 --> 29:05.880
Mrs. Fan! Steady yourself!

29:05.960 --> 29:07.760
Come on. Do it.

29:07.840 --> 29:09.480
Kill me!

29:13.120 --> 29:13.840
Mrs. Fan!

29:59.840 --> 30:02.520
-Smells amazing.
-Almost ready.

30:07.280 --> 30:08.880
Marquis, urgent news.

30:08.960 --> 30:10.600
Mrs. Fan has taken Sui Yuanqing.

30:14.000 --> 30:15.800
If you have the guts,
give me a clean death.

30:15.880 --> 30:17.080
One stroke!

30:17.800 --> 30:19.080
You are not worth that mercy.

30:19.160 --> 30:21.560
You lot think you can avenge Lin'an?

30:21.640 --> 30:23.160
You are nothing but useless trash.

30:23.240 --> 30:25.480
Say one more word and I will cut you down!

30:27.400 --> 30:30.320
-Orders from the Marquis. Don't interfere.
-Untie me!

30:31.440 --> 30:32.440
Tighter.

30:34.360 --> 30:35.320
That will do.

30:36.400 --> 30:37.440
Rebel scum!

30:38.480 --> 30:40.400
Open your eyes and look well.

30:41.120 --> 30:42.280
Your precious heir

30:42.960 --> 30:44.680
is in my hands!

30:45.760 --> 30:46.760
Shi Yue.

30:46.840 --> 30:49.520
It is His Highness. Do we rescue him?

30:52.920 --> 30:53.880
That is…

30:55.080 --> 30:56.280
Mrs. Fan.

30:57.400 --> 30:58.440
Preposterous.

30:59.040 --> 31:01.920
Has Xie Zheng already
seen through my scheme?

31:02.760 --> 31:06.160
Shi Yue, shall we lead troops
up the mountain now

31:06.240 --> 31:07.200
and seize His Highness back?

31:07.280 --> 31:08.240
No.

31:09.080 --> 31:10.880
Be careful of Xie Zheng's trap.

31:11.960 --> 31:14.560
I will take a detachment up
from the western path.

31:15.320 --> 31:16.760
You remain here and keep up the feint.

31:17.680 --> 31:18.600
Sound the horn.

31:19.560 --> 31:20.800
Sound the horn!

31:31.600 --> 31:34.040
What, afraid now?

31:34.640 --> 31:35.920
If you are scared, lower me down.

31:36.640 --> 31:38.000
When my army storms this mountain,

31:38.800 --> 31:40.280
I might even grant you a whole corpse.

31:50.080 --> 31:50.960
Look.

31:51.040 --> 31:52.360
Shi Yue moved first.

31:52.960 --> 31:54.560
Why only a small detachment?

31:55.560 --> 31:57.000
What is he playing at?

31:59.440 --> 32:02.120
The north backs into the mountain.
Three sides open to the plains.

32:02.880 --> 32:04.720
The west is clearly upwind.

32:05.520 --> 32:06.680
Yet he orders meat roasted

32:07.360 --> 32:08.960
only on the south and east.

32:10.440 --> 32:12.920
He is trying to stir unrest in our ranks.

32:13.840 --> 32:15.240
And he has another move waiting.

32:15.320 --> 32:16.840
Lure the tiger from its lair.

32:17.680 --> 32:20.320
He wants us walking
straight into his trap.

32:21.440 --> 32:22.480
Not without brains.

32:25.920 --> 32:27.640
So you are the precious heir?

32:30.080 --> 32:31.960
That was for my grandma.

32:32.040 --> 32:33.360
Lowborn trash.

32:33.440 --> 32:34.760
You dare--

32:34.840 --> 32:36.480
If not for you, you little cur,

32:36.560 --> 32:38.080
my mother would not be bedridden.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.280
You frightened her into paralysis.

32:39.360 --> 32:41.840
I was going to return in glory,
stay by her side,

32:41.920 --> 32:43.360
see her through her final days.

32:44.040 --> 32:45.080
Are you done yet?

32:45.880 --> 32:47.560
My little sister is crippled now.

32:47.640 --> 32:50.160
She should have had a better life ahead.

32:50.240 --> 32:51.160
Because of you,

32:51.240 --> 32:52.760
half her future is gone.

32:52.840 --> 32:54.840
-So we're not done here!
-Enough!

32:56.320 --> 32:57.840
What did we Lin'an folk ever do?

32:57.920 --> 32:59.880
You would not even
leave us the right to live.

33:02.800 --> 33:04.600
Pigs want to live too.

33:05.320 --> 33:06.400
What good does that do?

33:08.000 --> 33:09.800
They are slaughtered for meat.

33:09.880 --> 33:11.480
You lot

33:12.560 --> 33:14.560
are worth less than pigs.

33:16.720 --> 33:18.760
You are begging to die.

33:18.840 --> 33:19.680
Let me.

33:24.320 --> 33:28.520
Mrs. Fan's little show
has Shi Yue rattled.

33:28.600 --> 33:30.440
Even his finest tricks won't come to hand.

33:31.120 --> 33:33.920
Reckless, but it hit the mark.

33:34.600 --> 33:35.880
Shi Yue is cautious by nature.

33:36.960 --> 33:39.680
Seeing this, he will keep
the main army steady

33:40.280 --> 33:42.040
and lead a smaller force himself,

33:42.120 --> 33:43.760
looking for a chance to save Sui Yuanqing.

33:46.400 --> 33:47.680
Go on.

33:47.760 --> 33:49.080
Hit me.

33:49.160 --> 33:50.600
I like it when you hit me.

33:53.600 --> 33:54.440
Hit you?

33:55.640 --> 33:56.840
That was too light.

33:56.920 --> 33:58.160
Gag him.

34:00.280 --> 34:01.520
Let me.

34:02.200 --> 34:03.520
I have not bathed in five days anyway.

34:03.600 --> 34:05.200
Might be a bit pungent. Hold him still.

34:07.360 --> 34:09.600
Do not move. Stay still.

34:16.239 --> 34:17.560
Rebel scum!

34:18.400 --> 34:21.000
If you want your heir alive,

34:21.960 --> 34:24.199
bring meat and grain to trade!

34:30.719 --> 34:32.000
They cannot hear me.

34:37.360 --> 34:40.440
-If you want your heir alive,
-If you want your heir alive,

34:40.520 --> 34:43.480
-bring meat and grain to trade!
-bring meat and grain to trade!

34:46.159 --> 34:48.120
I pride myself on reading people,

34:48.199 --> 34:49.560
but your wife…

34:49.639 --> 34:51.120
I truly cannot figure her out.

34:54.159 --> 34:55.560
Xie Wu. Xie Qi.

34:55.639 --> 34:56.960
Stay with me.

34:57.040 --> 34:58.080
Xie Jiu.

34:58.160 --> 34:59.760
Go with Strategist and reinforce them.

34:59.840 --> 35:00.840
Yes.

35:00.920 --> 35:04.720
Ignoring us? I will thrash you to death.

35:06.800 --> 35:07.920
That is all you have?

35:09.760 --> 35:11.080
You have been collecting debts for years.

35:11.160 --> 35:12.920
Have you not learned something nastier?

35:13.000 --> 35:14.120
Something that truly humiliates?

35:15.880 --> 35:16.840
Yuanbao.

35:16.920 --> 35:18.240
I recall you telling us

35:18.840 --> 35:20.480
that if someone refuses to pay…

35:21.600 --> 35:23.360
-Hang them out to dry!
-Hang them out to dry!

35:23.440 --> 35:24.320
Deal with him.

35:27.200 --> 35:29.120
Belt. Take it off.

35:29.200 --> 35:32.040
-Do him.
-Come on. Let's have a look.

35:32.880 --> 35:34.120
Move him over. Come on.

35:34.200 --> 35:35.160
Ready?

35:36.280 --> 35:37.400
One, two, three.

35:40.280 --> 35:41.640
Look carefully!

35:43.000 --> 35:44.360
If you do not bring salt and meat,

35:45.520 --> 35:47.920
we will strip your heir bare!

35:48.000 --> 35:49.920
A man may die, but not be humiliated!

35:50.000 --> 35:51.040
I'm stripping him!

35:51.120 --> 35:53.120
This is Marquis Wu'an's bait.

35:53.840 --> 35:54.800
Wait.

35:55.560 --> 35:56.920
Wait a little longer.

35:58.240 --> 36:00.280
If you do not bring salt and meat,

36:00.880 --> 36:02.520
we will strip your heir bare!

36:03.920 --> 36:05.960
I mean it. I'm stripping him!

36:14.760 --> 36:15.880
If you do not bring it,

36:16.480 --> 36:19.040
your heir won't have an heir
to pass it on to!

36:32.080 --> 36:33.160
Stop!

36:37.520 --> 36:39.080
We will do as you say.

36:42.640 --> 36:43.520
General!

36:44.080 --> 36:44.920
General!

36:45.960 --> 36:47.080
Reporting to the General.

36:47.160 --> 36:49.120
General Shi Yue
orders the meat and grain sent up.

36:52.680 --> 36:53.840
Humiliating.

36:54.840 --> 36:55.960
Do as ordered!

37:03.800 --> 37:04.880
Do not hurt His Highness!

37:05.560 --> 37:06.720
Put everything into the baskets.

37:06.800 --> 37:08.320
Do not try anything.

37:11.400 --> 37:12.600
Move!

37:47.800 --> 37:48.720
A whole basket filled!

37:51.640 --> 37:52.480
Here. Over here.

37:53.640 --> 37:55.200
Do not bother with me!

37:55.280 --> 37:56.240
Xie Zheng is not here!

37:56.320 --> 37:58.200
Kill these lowborn wretches!

37:58.280 --> 37:59.760
His Highness commands it.

37:59.840 --> 38:00.960
Kill!

38:01.800 --> 38:04.800
Kill!

38:11.440 --> 38:12.400
Attack!

38:27.760 --> 38:28.960
Good!

38:29.040 --> 38:30.720
-We have food!
-We have food, folks!

38:30.800 --> 38:32.200
-Good!
-We did it!

38:33.720 --> 38:36.360
‎-Great!
‎-Well done!

38:36.440 --> 38:37.720
We are back!

38:37.800 --> 38:39.040
We are back!

38:39.120 --> 38:40.040
We did it!

38:40.800 --> 38:41.640
Look!

38:42.640 --> 38:44.600
-Look!
-Thirty roasted lambs,

38:44.680 --> 38:47.200
50 dan of grain, 50 jin of salt,
and three barrels of oil.

38:47.280 --> 38:49.120
Send everything to the fire unit.

38:49.200 --> 38:50.280
Let the men eat well tonight!

38:50.360 --> 38:51.600
Good!

38:51.680 --> 38:52.840
-Fan is formidable!
-Extra rations!

38:52.920 --> 38:55.600
Extra rations! Extra rations!

38:56.320 --> 38:57.160
Extra rations!

38:59.640 --> 39:01.520
OIL

39:07.960 --> 39:09.400
We pulled off another big one.

39:09.480 --> 39:10.920
Do you think we'll get rewarded again?

39:11.520 --> 39:13.480
I only ask one thing of Marquis Wu'an.

39:13.560 --> 39:15.440
When we drive the enemy back,

39:15.520 --> 39:17.400
hand Sui Yuanqing over to us.

39:17.480 --> 39:19.480
Let us decide how he dies.

39:19.560 --> 39:20.400
Good.

39:20.480 --> 39:21.880
Yes, we will all ask together.

39:21.960 --> 39:23.120
Together.

39:24.640 --> 39:25.640
General Xie Wu.

39:25.720 --> 39:28.360
Sui Yuanqing bought us quite a feast.

39:28.440 --> 39:29.640
Where is Yan Zheng?

39:29.720 --> 39:31.520
There is lamb. It will help him recover.

39:32.680 --> 39:34.320
Mrs. Fan, the Marquis wishes to see you.

39:36.400 --> 39:38.040
So soon?

39:38.120 --> 39:39.520
What, another reward?

39:41.080 --> 39:42.400
Hand over your weapons first.

39:47.280 --> 39:48.600
Why?

39:48.680 --> 39:50.240
No weapons inside the tent.

39:54.200 --> 39:55.040
Here.

39:59.000 --> 40:00.960
What is going on? Where is Yan Zheng?

40:02.480 --> 40:04.800
You will see him
after meeting the Marquis.

40:07.560 --> 40:08.400
Come.

40:21.720 --> 40:23.920
Marquis, Fan Changyu
and her men have arrived.

40:26.320 --> 40:29.440
Commoner Fan Changyu greets Marquis Wu'an.

40:29.520 --> 40:31.000
We greet the Marquis.

40:35.680 --> 40:36.560
Fan Changyu.

40:37.240 --> 40:39.800
You acted without orders.
That warrants severe punishment

40:40.880 --> 40:41.720
by military law.

40:45.880 --> 40:47.720
Acted… without orders.

40:48.400 --> 40:51.280
Marquis, though we moved on our own,

40:51.360 --> 40:52.320
we rendered merit.

40:52.920 --> 40:54.400
Please judge fairly.

40:56.200 --> 40:57.960
When you stand within the army,

40:58.040 --> 41:00.640
you have to abide by its laws.

41:00.720 --> 41:03.280
If I excuse you today
for acting without orders,

41:03.360 --> 41:05.760
greater trouble will follow tomorrow.

41:09.080 --> 41:11.800
All right. Then punish me alone.

41:11.880 --> 41:13.160
They followed because of me.

41:13.880 --> 41:15.640
No one forced us. We chose to go.

41:15.720 --> 41:17.240
If there is punishment, we share it.

41:17.320 --> 41:18.440
-Yes.
-That's right.

41:18.520 --> 41:20.880
Marquis, we earned military merit.

41:21.920 --> 41:25.520
Fan Changyu sought the meat
to strengthen the wounded.

41:26.240 --> 41:27.360
We ask you to see clearly.

41:27.440 --> 41:28.680
Please judge fairly.

41:36.240 --> 41:37.080
Marquis.

41:42.480 --> 41:44.080
I humbly request that.

41:44.680 --> 41:45.880
Fan Changyu is my wife.

41:46.600 --> 41:47.560
if punishment is due,

41:48.080 --> 41:49.520
I will bear it with her.

41:49.600 --> 41:51.640
Why are you here? You are injured.

41:51.720 --> 41:53.160
Do not speak recklessly.

41:55.880 --> 41:57.720
Article 27 of the Military Code.

41:58.520 --> 42:00.920
Acting without orders.

42:01.640 --> 42:04.280
-What is the prescribed penalty?
-Thirty strokes.

42:07.720 --> 42:10.600
In light of Fan Changyu's merit
in breaching the dam,

42:10.680 --> 42:13.040
her delivery of grain,
and this being her first offense,

42:13.640 --> 42:15.960
reduce it to 20 strokes,
as warning to others.

42:16.040 --> 42:18.680
Marquis, grant me leave
to accept the punishment

42:19.560 --> 42:20.720
in her stead.

42:25.440 --> 42:26.680
No! Absolutely not!

42:26.760 --> 42:29.120
Marquis, I take responsibility
for what I did.

42:29.200 --> 42:31.400
-Punish me alone.
-Marquis, I beg you.

42:34.320 --> 42:35.480
I…

42:36.880 --> 42:38.280
Marquis, I was wrong.

42:39.480 --> 42:41.680
My husband knew nothing of this.

42:41.760 --> 42:42.760
Punish only me.

42:42.840 --> 42:44.840
Then… what would you have me do?

42:44.920 --> 42:45.800
Your Lordship knows

42:46.880 --> 42:48.160
orders are iron.

42:48.880 --> 42:50.560
Defying them merits death.

42:57.360 --> 42:59.240
Your Lordship must be fair
in reward and punishment.

42:59.320 --> 43:00.640
Issue the order.

43:00.720 --> 43:01.800
Punish me alone.

43:02.400 --> 43:03.600
Marquis, punish me!

43:03.680 --> 43:05.600
-Marquis, punish us together!
-Yes!

43:05.680 --> 43:06.560
-Yes!
-Together!

43:06.640 --> 43:07.640
We accept it together!

43:07.720 --> 43:09.800
Orders are iron. This is not a game.

43:14.560 --> 43:15.560
Marquis.

43:16.280 --> 43:17.120
Give the order.

43:22.120 --> 43:24.480
This is not how we agreed it would go.

43:25.360 --> 43:26.840
-Guards!
-Here.

43:26.920 --> 43:28.880
Punish Yan Zheng alone.

43:28.960 --> 43:29.960
Yes.

43:30.040 --> 43:30.960
-No!
-Carry it out!

43:31.040 --> 43:33.320
Marquis, my husband truly knew nothing!

43:35.440 --> 43:37.120
-Marquis!
-Stand back!

46:15.400 --> 46:18.400
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS FILM

46:18.480 --> 46:19.360
Subtitle translation by: Jiaxin Wang
